data.title: Aurora Mobile (JG.US) partners with Zhangjiakou Bank to write a new chapter in digital transformation with JPush push.
data.meta_description: Today,as the digital wave sweeps the world, the banking industry is undergoing profound changes at an unprecedented speed. As a leading local city commercial bank, Zhangjiakou Bank keeps pace with the times, actively responds to the national development strategy, and is committed to improving its financial service capabilities through digital transformation to better serve urban and rural residents, small and medium-sized enterprises, and the local economy. In this process, JPush, with its professional customer interaction and marketing technology services, has become a solid partner of Zhangjiakou Bank on the path of digital transformation. As a local city commercial bank, Zhangjiakou Bank has been serving urban and rural residents, small and medium-sized enterprises, and promoting local economic development.
